flowchart TD
    A[Summary request received] --> B[Profile classification small medium large]
    B --> C[Compute request fingerprint and policy context]
    C --> D{Force regenerate?}
    D -- Yes --> H[Skip reuse and go to provider path]
    D -- No --> E{Identical reuse eligible and fresh <= 24h?}
    E -- Yes --> F[Return reused summary]
    E -- No --> G{Near-identical policy enabled and fresh <= 30m?}
    G -- Yes --> F
    G -- No --> H

    H --> I[Start endpoint budget timer]
    I --> J[Provider attempt 1]
    J --> K{Success?}
    K -- Yes --> L[Quality guardrail checks]
    L --> M{Checks pass?}
    M -- Yes --> N[Persist generated summary]
    M -- No --> O[Return deterministic fallback]

    K -- No transient --> P{Remaining budget supports one retry?}
    P -- Yes --> Q[Retry once with bounded jitter backoff]
    Q --> R{Retry success?}
    R -- Yes --> L
    R -- No --> O
    P -- No --> O

    K -- No terminal --> O

    F --> S[Emit trace outcome reused_artifact]
    N --> T[Emit trace outcome generation]
    O --> U[Emit trace outcome fallback_timeout or fallback_error]

    S --> V[Return SummaryUiResponse or SummaryResponse]
    T --> V
    U --> V
